-02-13T14:22:56.000Z","msg":"依d書全部有中文版~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"睇英文對新手會唔會好難明？"},{"pid":"3943da0ce51569b0efb7e052b7db7e1d6c3e1d7a","tid":1019923,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"54f2a827946df816416f3c83d26503226116a9ce","tid":1019923,"uid":27340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bd09c331966171d6bf0e50d0a46ac80c53daebd","tid":1019923,"uid":51297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e125d84ea873161dfada206e1461400825ac2ce","tid":1019923,"uid":30113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"買左快思慢想2-3年，但都淨係擺無睇到。<br />\n我同自己講一定會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係都想問下樓主覺得睇完本書有冇對自己的decision-making procese帶來正面影響?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得有的，日常嘅就小小。但因爲我搞D 生意仔，識入面嘅野對SET 定價一類野幾有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"可唔可以再講詳細啲點樣應用<br />\n幾經辛苦終於睇晒本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有啲位睇得唔通<br />\n唔知要點樣應用好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf227a69bd4a22ef74c29587d5c595612ca08660","tid":1019923,"uid":182401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  intro to psy 本 textbook 就係最好嘅入門書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812af2e5d09d3649c88a10f821bd972f53fe7a33","tid":1019923,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}